import React from 'react'
import {ChakraProvider, Container, Box, Stack, Text, Heading, Center} from '@chakra-ui/react'

const Header = () => {
    const header_border = {
        borderBottom: "1px solid #38444D",
      };
    return (
        <ChakraProvider>
            <Container>
                <Center>
                <Box style={header_border}>
                <Stack direction="row" spacing="400px" >
                    <Box>
                        <Text fontSize="19px" fontWeight="800" color="#FFFFFF" mt="10px">Home</Text>
                    </Box>
                    <Box>
                        <Text  w="23px" h="23px"  bg="tomato" mt="15px">.</Text>
                    </Box>
                </Stack>
                </Box>
                </Center>
            </Container>
        </ChakraProvider>
    )
}


export default Header
